# game/Day5.rpy:3574
translate russian ragcheckpoint_b95c532d:

    # "Or a smirk from Jax as I wander, alone, through the culture fair."
    "Или ухмылку Джекса, пока брожу один(-на) по культурному фестивалю."

# game/Day5.rpy:3576
translate russian ragcheckpoint_c433f61e:

    # "But by far what hurts the most"
    "Но больнее всего"

# game/Day5.rpy:3578
translate russian ragcheckpoint_0d8ed4f4:

    # "is the look of quiet pain whenever Ragatha’s gaze meets mine across the culture festival."
    "взгляд тихой боли, когда взгляды с Рагатой пересекаются через весь фестиваль."

# game/Day5.rpy:3580
translate russian ragcheckpoint_a8ac44bf:

    # "I take it all in what is, hopefully, dignified silence."
